      <scopecontent id="aspace_5c6ac07fd38ade0e2fd5607dc8f7d7a6">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection provides an overview of the work of a Yale Divinity School graduate who served Congregational churches from 1948 to 1985. Sermons, prayers, and programs are arranged chronologically in looseleaf notebooks.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
